Credits fully to this nice vim-cast:
http://vimcasts.org/episodes/synchronizing-plugins-with-git-submodules-and-pathogen/

Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/phani-vadrevu/awesome-dot-rc.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/screenrc ~/.vimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
